snippet.title: Ferrari Virtual Academy - Official Trailer - Motoroids.com
snippet.description: Ferrari is giving petrolheads a chance to get behind the virtual wheel of the F10 F1 car on three iconic tracks - Fiorano, Mugello and the Nürburgring. More info on Motoroids.com. Visit www.ferrarivirtualacademy.com to download the app of 9th September 2010.
